---
title: Seared Fillet Steak & Balsamic Mushrooms with Thyme-Roasted Veggies & Pear-Parmesan Salad
description: To accompany your tender premium fillet steak, we've got mushrooms cooked with garlic and butter, plus elegant roasted
veggies and a sweet and savoury salad. Get ready to serve up a feast!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
